    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen ASME V&V 40 credibility factors are assessed and meet or exceed required levels for the elevated Model Risk Level 3 designation. The equivalency of input parameters factor is recorded as not-assessed based on the team's judgment that the boundary condition mapping is self-evident. The overall credibility evidence is considered sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
